en_6704227_0	A police investigation is underway after a fuel station in Akuressa, Matara was allegedly robbed by two foreigners.
en_6704227_1	The foreigners had allegedly walked into the fuel station under the guise of customers at around 3.00 pm on Monday.
en_6704227_2	Our reporter reveals that after purchasing items from the station the suspects had robbed money and fled the scene in a three-wheeler.
en_6704227_3	Subsequent, to the robbery the suspects are believed to have headed to Mirissa area, according to our reporter.
en_6704227_4	Newsfirst has received the CCTV footage of the incident, that was recorded at the time of the robbery.
